{"tid":1199103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11環保團體響應6．12罷市反修例","createTime":"2019-06-10T11:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T11:53:00.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a02d1c33386e4382a74cc2c867d0bae5f3016bf5","tid":1199103,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190610/s00001/8af51ec0d0cba675d699e61a28f3ce2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190610%2Fs00001%2F8af51ec0d0cba675d699e61a28f3ce2d.jpg&h=82556076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民陣昨（9日）發起遊行，反對修訂《逃犯條例》，稱有103萬人參加，特區政府其後發稿表示，修例草案會如期在周三（12日）恢復二讀，有網民發起周三罷工、罷市及罷課。11個環保團體今日（10日）宣布響應罷市，將於周三停工一天。<br />\n<br />\n環保觸覺、綠領行動、守護大嶼聯盟、創建香港、香港自然生態論壇、龍尾環境教育中心、自然脈絡、香港海豚保育學會、大嶼山愛護水牛協會及土地正義聯盟，聯合發出聲明，就政府在百萬市民遊行後仍「對撤回修訂《逃犯條例》充耳不聞」，表示憤怒及遺憾，故宣布於周三停止辦公一天，方便員工參與當日的反修例行動。<br />\n<br />\n另外，綠色力量開設的facebook專頁「回收俠&mdash;&mdash;紙包飲品盒回收 Drink Carton Recycling」亦發帖，宣布綠色力量周三會「休息」一天，響應反修例行動。"},{"pid":"f3b58c90e1a14d93d7479f33ade94336971a2393","tid":1199103,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190610/s00001/1560165309357/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190610%2Fs00001%2F1560165309357%2F&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3XtwyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=048d0d1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190610%2Fs00001%2F1560165309357%2F&h=3e0a9d36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190610/s00001/1560165309357/</a>"},{"pid":"a0b797d7b9a1578c6af5a8cbf8379463894d96fc","tid":1199103,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:51:23.000Z","msg":"乜呢啲團體當自己做生意㗎？<br />\nBtw 支持多啲人罷市"},{"pid":"aea4d24358c82f3ec4a53390c144f575bcc1af87","tid":1199103,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"有人全職收錢幫大嶼山愛護水牛協會打工架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}